				<Property Name="{852f0cdd-61b3-4c6c-894a-90212b6cc24e}">
If DMG04  value is Divorced, it will be represented as D. Legally Separated will be X, Married will be M, Registered Domestic Partner will be B, Separated will be S, Single will be I, Widowed will be W, Unmarried will be U, and Unreported will be R.</Property>
